The imitators simply add a couple of letters to register their trademarks.
In this way, Gucci becomes Lu-Gucci and instead of Prada, Prada-Kny is registered.
German companies are also legally copied in the same way, as happened with the sportswear manufacturer Puma.
Pattloch opens a filing cabinet where he keeps seats from the Beijing trademark office.
